OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny heavy
OL,6,Fshowers will soon clear eastwards,
OL,7,Fleaving a largely dry night with clear
OL,8,Fspells developing for a time. Staying
OL,9,Fgenerally cloudy across western areas,
OL,10,Fwith a few light showers. A mild and
OL,11,Fbreezy night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FIncreasingly cloudy, ahead
OL,14,Fof a band of rain sweeping east across
OL,15,Fthe region. Sunny spells and blustery
OL,16,Fshowers in the afternoon, with hail
OL,17,Fand thunder. Showers persisting in the
OL,18,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
