OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FBreezy on Thursday, with sunny spells
OL,7,Fand showers, heavy and thundery. Fewer
OL,8,Fshowers likely on Friday. Drier on
OL,9,FSaturday, but still the chance of a
OL,10,Ffew showers. Staying cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
